      "url": "https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/07/07/ant-groups-robbyant-open-sources-lingbot-vision-a-1b-boundary-centric-vision-foundation-model-for-dense-spatial-perception",
      "source": "AIHOT · MarkTechPost（RSS）",
